<footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-content">
        <div class="footer-cta reveal">
            <p class="footer-tagline">"Concentrate, Record, and Grow."</p>
            <p class="footer-desc">
                PomoCal은 macOS 사용자를 위한 가장 직관적인 학습 관리
                도구입니다.<br />
                오늘 할 일을 정하고 타이머를 시작하세요. 나머지는 PomoCal이 당신의
                시스템 캘린더에 완벽하게 기록해 드립니다.
            </p>
            <a
                href="https://github.com/pxxguin/PomodoroCalendar/releases"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn btn-primary"
            >
                <svg
                    width="18"
                    height="18"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                    fill="none"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M17.5 12.5V15.8333C17.5 16.2754 17.3244 16.6993 17.0118 17.0118C16.6993 17.3244 16.2754 17.5 15.8333 17.5H4.16667C3.72464 17.5 3.30072 17.3244 2.98816 17.0118C2.67559 16.6993 2.5 16.2754 2.5 15.8333V12.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                    <path
                        d="M5.83337 8.33337L10 12.5L14.1667 8.33337"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                    <path
                        d="M10 12.5V2.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
                지금 다운로드하기
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <img
                    src="/images/app-icon.png"
                    alt="PomoCal"
                    class="footer-logo"
                />
                <span>PomoCal</span>
            </div>
            <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 PomoCal. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a
                    href="https://github.com/pxxguin/PomodoroCalendar"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="footer-link"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="18"
                        height="18"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                    GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .footer {
        background: var(--color-bg);
        padding: var(--space-5xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .footer-content {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-cta {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
        padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .footer-tagline {
        font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--color-text-primary);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .footer-desc {
        font-size: var(--font-size-base);
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.8;
        max-width: 540px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .footer-bottom {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .footer-brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }

    .footer-logo {
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .footer-copy {
        font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
        color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    }

    .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .footer-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .footer-link:hover {
        color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .footer-tagline {
            font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
        }

        .footer-desc br {
            display: none;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: var(--space-md);
        }
    }
</style>
